    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "This 1994 Toyota Supra Turbo represents a rare opportunity to own an unmolested, investment-grade A80 icon. Powered by the legendary 2JZ-GTE 3.0L twin-scroll inline-six, the engine remains in factory configuration, delivering smooth, sequential boost through the original intercooler system. The drivetrain features the coveted Getrag V160 6-speed manual transmission and a factory Torsen limited-slip differential, ensuring optimal torque distribution. The chassis is impeccably preserved, retaining its original double-wishbone suspension geometry and high-performance braking system with zero aftermarket modifications. Every component, from the DOHC valvetrain to the pristine undercarriage, reflects a vehicle maintained to the highest mechanical standards. This is a purist's example, offering the precise tactile feedback and over-engineered reliability that defined the peak of the JDM era.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 11
    },
    {
