    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offered is a collector-grade E46 M3, a pinnacle of BMW M-division engineering. This specimen features the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, boasting individual throttle bodies and a high-pressure dual-VANOS system that has been meticulously serviced for optimal cam timing. Power is managed via a Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and delivered through a limited-slip differential with a 3.62 final drive ratio. The chassis integrity is absolute; the rear subframe has been proactively reinforced, and the suspension retains its factory-spec MacPherson strut front and multi-link rear configuration with all bushings in pristine, compliant condition. Mechanical upkeep is current, with the rod bearing recall addressed and the valves recently shimmed to factory tolerances. This is an uncompromising, turn-key machine for the discerning purist.",
